{
  "stem": "16395.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But she never let them go out from the house until she borrowed it from the next door neighbor-- I should go to the movie with them.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She was very, very lovable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Very nice parents I had.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the holidays and Shabbat, everybody was religious.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't such a thing that somebody didn't have any [? cows ?] or anything.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So everybody stayed home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We used to make a cholent Friday and send it over to the baker.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and Saturday, noontime, we used to take it out from the baker.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My mother used to pay for it Friday.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then we needed tea.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we went to one place a little bit further.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, this was everything on the same street.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We lived on the nicest street in this town.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I used to go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I used to go bring tea-- not the tea, just the water.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She cooked it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we paid ahead of time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then we bring-- we brought [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we had tea with the cholent, with some meat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "One day, she sent me for the cholent.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I'll tell you a-- a funny story.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And old cholent looked the same way, because they were-- my mother already recognized her-- her thing, what she put it into.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I brought home, and my mother looked at it, and she said, oh, my god.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "That's not mine.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And she took it fast back and brought ours.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was some meat and potatoes, that's all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They lived in the same town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they got married.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They lived in another town.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But when they got married, my mother had-- I told you, was a [? tree ?] family.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
